&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ward Clerk – Cedar Ward&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;22hpw&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has become available on Cedar Ward and we are able to have extended ward clerk cover from 8am – 8pm, five days a week. We are looking for another ward clerk to job share. The days of work will be Thursday and Friday from 8am – 8 pm. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be the first point of call for patients and their family/carers in addition to supporting our multidisciplinary team. We require applicants with experience of working in the NHS, preferably as a ward clerk or in a patient facing administrative role, familiar with NHS IT systems and processes.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information please contact Sue Hardy (Lead Nurse for Stroke) (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;susan.hardy5@nhs.net/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; 01932 722206) or Boby Sebastian (Ward Manager for Stroke) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;boby.sebastian@nhs.net/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; 01932 723249)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
